<section class="views-element-container w3-block w3-block-wrapper block-views block-views-blockcommentary-slider-block-1" id="block-views-block-commentary-slider-block-1">
  
    
          <div class="w3-row element-container-wrapper"><div class="w3-row view view-commentary-slider view-id-commentary_slider view-display-id-block_1 js-view-dom-id-fd122aa3e9cb4ecd6180ae41d8d84f5f961647a5a5064624190dbd484362fbf9">
  
    
      <header class="view-header">
      <div class="slider-info">
        <h2>
American, Woman, Development Economist
        </h2>
        <h6>
         These episodes are meant to capture the role of luck and privilege in my life, as an American during America’s near-hegemon years, and as a woman in a period of growing opportunities for women. 
        </h6>
      </div>
    </header>
      
